    {
      "id": "671a44e4aff09e00003d7e95",
      "text": "\t[~ 昨年、年度、年夜？古夜？？？]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1729774821,
      "updated": 1729774821
    },
    {
      "id": "6721f13ec9ec6a0000b5c762",
      "text": "\t [~ 昨今、今夜、古今、今度？][cak.icon]",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1730277695,
      "updated": 1730277697
    },
    {
      "id": "671a442eaff09e00003d7e90",
      "text": "\t[~ 里芋、里山、首里？万里？]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1729774638,
      "updated": 1729774729
    },
    {
      "id": "671a447eaff09e00003d7e92",
      "text": "\t[~ 丸と四角の違いは何？？]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1729774718,
      "updated": 1729774805
    },
    {
      "id": "671a44c8aff09e00003d7e94",
      "text": "\t[~ 回答が大阪市営地下鉄の駅名になる可能性はある]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1729774793,
      "updated": 1729774855
    },
    {
      "id": "6721f148c9ec6a0000b5c763",
      "text": "\t[~ 悪玉、温玉、玉石、玉座 ？][cak.icon]",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1730277705,
      "updated": 1730277708
